<DIV1 TYPE="publisher's conclusion">
<PB N="58" REF="60" MS="y">
<HEAD>CONCLUSION by the Publi&s;her.</HEAD>
<P>WHile this was at the Pre&s;s, and the Co|py thus far fini&s;h'd, the Author was &s;eiz'd with a violent Fit of an Apoplexy, whereby he was di&s;abled fini&s;hing what he de|&s;ign'd in his farther Defence, and continuing now for above Six Weeks in a Weak and Langui&s;hing Condition, neither able to go on, or likely to recover, at lea&s;t in any &s;hort time, his Friends thought it not fit to delay the Publication of this any longer; if he recovers, he may be able to fini&s;h what he began; if not, it is the Opinion of mo&s;t that know him, that the Treatment which he here complains of, and &s;ome others that he would have &s;poken of, have been the apparent Cau&s;e of his Di&s;a&s;ter.</P>
<TRAILER>FINIS.</TRAILER>
